{"type": "article", "id": 9779, "title": "Light Phone 极简手机", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-20T07:12:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125812DrwmlNvVOnG54HsW.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Light Phone 是一款“反智能”的手机，它诞生于谷歌 30 Weeks 发起的设计师孵化器，来自艺术家Joe Holler 和产品设计师 Kaiwei Tang。这款手机能做什么？答案是除了接打电话什么都不能。一次充电后可以满足 20 天左右的续航。“返璞归真”的手机不管从概念还是产品来讲都不少见，但能做的这么好看的还真不多。目前产品售价 100 美元，正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，感兴趣的话可以<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/thelightphone/the-light-phone\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里支持</a>。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125809v9wUCT4WkYInxpRo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74572127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021258095E0uKdorx1DImkNA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125809oXZUxPYrjvsW7t6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64792176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021258102gmOIlLX9r3ApYKs.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63325183\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125810786gHwsyrcNh2fkd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63447433\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125812AyVZT6XO2eS1PkCW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}